OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1778166668
OL,3,CTeenager admits possessing explosives
OL,4,Cand threatening to bomb college
OL,6,FStaffordshire Police have released
OL,7,Ffootage of Jagger Strang being
OL,8,Farrested and then being further
OL,9,Farrested later on in the day.
OL,11,FA teenager has admitted possessing
OL,12,Fexplosive substances and threatening
OL,13,Fto bomb a college.
OL,15,FJagger Strang, 18, from Stafford, was
OL,16,Fdue to go on trial for nine offences
OL,17,Fon Wednesday at Leicester Crown Court.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1778166668
OL,3,CTeenager admits possessing explosives
OL,4,Cand threatening to bomb college
OL,6,FOn the morning of the trial, Strang
OL,7,Fpleaded guilty to seven charges,
OL,8,Fincluding possession of explosive
OL,9,Fsubstances gunpower and thermite, and
OL,10,Faccessing YouTube videos about the
OL,11,Fmanufacture of black powder and how to
OL,12,Fmake a detonator from improvised
OL,13,Fmaterials.
OL,15,FHe also admitted making threats to
OL,16,Fkill peers at Stafford College and set
OL,17,Foff a bomb there in September last
OL,18,Fyear.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1778166668
OL,3,CTeenager admits possessing explosives
OL,4,Cand threatening to bomb college
OL,6,FThe court heard Strang had pleaded
OL,7,Fguilty on the basis that "he had no
OL,8,Fintention to build a bomb".
OL,10,FThe pleas were accepted by
OL,11,Fprosecutors, who said they would not
OL,12,Fbe proceeding with a trial for the
OL,13,Fremaining charges.
OL,15,FIn September 2025, officers were
OL,16,Fcontacted by a safeguarding officer at
OL,17,FStafford College following reports
OL,18,Fthat Strang, who was a student at the
OL,19,Fcollege, had told other students he
OL,20,Fhad numerous weapons and had plans to
OL,21,Fblow up the site.
OL,26,@oD@ZOUpD@ZO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1778166668
OL,3,CTeenager admits possessing explosives
OL,4,Cand threatening to bomb college
OL,6,FStrang was arrested at his home
OL,7,Faddress the same day. During a search
OL,8,Fof the property, officers seized a
OL,9,Fnumber of chemicals along with
OL,10,Fhomemade black powder/gunpowder and
OL,11,Fthermite. A blow pipe was also
OL,12,Frecovered.
OL,14,FOfficers also examined Strang's mobile
OL,15,Fphone, where they found concerning
OL,16,Fmaterial including a manifesto, as
OL,17,Fwell as a series of recent internet
OL,18,Fsearches relating to notorious mass
OL,19,Fkillers and instructions on how to
OL,20,Fmake bombs and remote detonators.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1778166668
OL,3,CTeenager admits possessing explosives
OL,4,Cand threatening to bomb college
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Dave Rowlands
OL,7,Fsaid: "This was a deeply concerning
OL,8,Fcase involving threats that
OL,9,Funderstandably caused significant
OL,10,Falarm to the students that Strang
OL,11,Ftalked to and staff at the college.
OL,12,FThanks to the vigilance of the
OL,13,Fcollege's students and staff and the
OL,14,Fswift actions of our officers, we were
OL,15,Fable to intervene quickly and prevent
OL,16,Fany potential harm.
OL,26,@oD@GOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1778166668
OL,3,CTeenager admits possessing explosives
OL,4,Cand threatening to bomb college
OL,6,F"We take all reports of this nature
OL,7,Fextremely seriously. The outcome of
OL,8,Fthis case demonstrates our commitment
OL,9,Fto working closely with partner
OL,10,Fagencies to identify risks early and
OL,11,Fto take robust action to protect the
OL,12,Fpublic."
OL,14,FStrang is due to be sentenced on 29
OL,15,FJune at Birmingham Crown Court.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@HO]
